org.spongepowered.api.data.manipulator.mutable.entity

Interface BodyPartRotationalData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataManipulator<BodyPartRotationalData,ImmutableBodyPartRotationalData>, DataSerializable, ValueContainer<BodyPartRotationalData>

    public interface BodyPartRotationalData
extends DataManipulator<BodyPartRotationalData,ImmutableBodyPartRotationalData>
    Represents the mapped rotational data for all known body parts. Usually applicable to Humanoids and ArmorStands.
